=== 7. RECOVERY: Restart RabbitMQ ===
a4-rabbitmq-1


=== 8. POST-RECOVERY: Trigger another sensor update ===
{"id":"sensor-001","name":"Living Room Thermostat","type":"temperature","location":"living_room","value":88,"unit":"fahrenheit","status":"active","last_reading":"2026-04-17T16:00:13Z","created_at":"2026-04-13T04:38:36Z","updated_at":"2026-04-17T16:00:13Z"}
